## power-domains

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>` encoded as a list of phandle + power-domain-specifier pairs

A list of phandle and power domain specifier pairs, one per power domain consumed by the device. The number of cells in each power domain specifier is determined by the `#power-domain-cells` property of the referenced power domain provider node.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    power-domains = <&rpmhpd RPMHPD_CX>;
};
```
